description:
CHANGE OF RAIMENT | Episode 1 | Naked and Unashamed - A Presentation On Modesty | Hilari Henriques
There are three corrections that I need to make as it relates to references given in the study. Please forgive me for the mistakes and correct them in your notes.
1. At minute marker 1:23, I referenced 2 Timothy  3:16 and 17, but said 1 Timothy. It should be 2 Timothy
2. Around minute marker 12:17, a slide was put up with a reference for 6T 636; It should be 4T 636
3. Around minute marker 33:34 onward, I shared the wrong reference. It should not be Leviticus 13; but rather Leviticus 20:17-21.
Thank you for your understanding 

I will, by Gods grace, make these corrections publicly in our next study.
